data.description: Step into comfort in this Tuscumbia home with three bedrooms and two baths. The open living vaulted space and well-equipped kitchen, with granite countertops, create a cozy hub for family or friends. The master suite is a private retreat, boasting a large tiled shower. The fenced backyard is perfect for outdoor fun. Plus, there's a dedicated storm shelter for added safety. Close to schools, it's a great spot for anyone looking for a comfy modern haven. Welcome to a home where style meets ease – your perfect place!
